**What they want from this post:** Visual inspiration that is specific enough to actually use — not generic goth nail roundups with one silver nail mixed in. They want to see the distinction between sub-aesthetics, find a specific image that matches what they have in their head, and either screenshot it for their nail tech or save it to their Pinterest board.

